Didem Unat @ Koc University 

Credit: Mark Harris - NVIDIA Corporation

Description:
A simple 1D Stencil code useful (basis for many PDE solvers).

1st kernel: stencil_1D_simple 
Performs stencil with a radius 3 on 1D array

2nd kernel: stencil_1D_improved
Uses shared memory to eliminate redundant memory accesses
Fix the problems in the code one by one
